    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/7e957d8959d2a2ca2ac67bc19ec31e5d.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=246 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/d5ec2bacbb4eac32a3764f5c41269f69.avif?t=1769702616\" width=1232 height=706 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到《污痕圣杯：阿瓦隆的陨落》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进<strong>《污痕圣杯：阿瓦隆的陨落》</strong>的世界，在这款成熟的第一人称视角开放世界RPG中，你将见证一个将亚瑟王传说重新诠释的黑暗世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索错综复杂的主线剧情，自亚瑟王的统治结束已经过去整整600年，在经历了无尽的纷争之后，你终于有机会重塑他留下的遗产。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏是一封献给开放世界第一人称RPG的情书。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/b0f72262a160955ec04154b65de8b902.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=280 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关键特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●     <strong>海量游戏内容</strong>：在三个广阔区域中享受50-70小时的精彩游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●     <strong>错综复杂的叙事</strong>：引人入胜的主线剧情与数百个支线任务，结交无数个性鲜明而且拥有配音对话的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●     <strong>自由的游玩风格</strong>：利用不计其数的搭配来打造属于自己的独特游玩体验：组合不同的属性、技能与装备来创造你最喜欢的配置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/45f65f6c2e54bd71e3b1101058cafcc4.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿瓦隆将带来数不尽的奥秘与发现：隐藏物品、秘密剧情、独特敌人、地牢、任务以及有趣的NPC角色。随心所欲自由探索，在这款货真价实的开放世界中开辟自己的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/b7c07063b503c5dab520df9df09072af.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无缝切换近战武器、盾牌、弓箭、魔法、投掷物、混合物以及其他物品。利用闪避、招架与格挡化险为夷。尝试独一无二的终极战斗风格，想方设法战胜各方强敌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/db3a721771e24918f1aa08709bda8f20.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借琳琅满目的属性、特性、装备以及制作选择，随心所欲塑造想要的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想成为一个疯狂的炼金术士狂战士，近身肉搏？行。<br>或者是一个可以召唤亡灵大军的神秘铁匠法师？没问题。<br>还是一名徘徊于阴影之中的潜行弓箭手？无需多言，这款游戏绝对能让所有潜行弓狂热分子心满意足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/c7f050308040db53fc53527c20d11174.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >领略三个截然不同的区域，见证形形色色的任务、NPC角色、物品以及更多内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●     迷雾重重的<strong>Horns of the South</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●     阳光明媚的<strong>Cuanacht Village</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●     <strong>Forlorn Swords</strong>冰封山巅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/00b8e6d14368ebaf9881ea4c8ea4816d.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在阿瓦隆这个栩栩如生的世界中，你的旅程永远不会乏味。参与包括素描绘画、钓鱼、耕种、锻造、炼金、烹饪、采矿、房屋管理在内的丰富活动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/d4eebeab0711e20908f547ea8caafdb1.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临，混沌的原始力量Wyrdness踏上这片大地，扭曲现实的本质。敌人们将变得更加凶狠，一旦犹豫犯错便会追悔莫及。杀戮或者被杀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1466060/extras/9262011317315c32fec88ac9cd74ae4b.avif?t=1769702616\" width=700 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对难以抉择的道德困境，这些艰难的抉择将考验你的人格并塑造阿瓦隆的未来。跟随亚瑟·潘德拉贡国王的黑暗遗产，结交超过250名NPC角色并挑战200+支线任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
